Utterance.UttText: on bed 2, Yoana Harrison, 55 years old under Dr Garcia, she is our new admission.
She came in with severe vomiting and nausea for 2 days.
She feels very weak. the doctors have not done their rounds yet so awaiting review.
She is ambulant and self caring but may need some standby assist as she might be a high falls risk as she feels very weak.
Maybe we can ask the doctors to give her some hydration when they come in for their rounds.
